quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,103,"Ne toto khwamanya mbu balaboola mbu: “Omundu niye umwechesinjia” ulusungo lwa ulia owabamanyinjia nilweshicheni, niluno ni olusungo lweshiarabu lwa habulafu."
  16,104,"Toto balia balasuubilanga tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye tawe, Nyasaye shabalunjisinjia tawe, ne balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu."
  16,105,"Balia abachikhanga obubeyi ni balia abalasuubilanga ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye tawe, ne abo nibo ababeyi."
  16,106,"Ulia ukhaya Nyasaye namalilenje okhusuubila, halali ulia unichilisibwe ne omwoyo kwaye nikubunile po khubusubili, ne ulia wikulilanga eshilifu shishie obukhayi, obusinyifu bwa Nyasaye buli khubo, ne balinyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo."
  16,107,"Endio nilwokhuba mbu bo bachama obulamu bwokhushialo okhushila obulamu bwomwikulu. Ne toto Nyasaye shalunjisinjia Abandu abakhayi tawe."
  16,108,"Abo nibo aba Nyasaye yasuba emioyo chiabu nende tsimbulililo tsiabu nende tsindolelo tsiabu. Ne abo nibo abakaandala."
  16,109,"Inganakani ibulaho tawe, abo nibo balibula obukhala mwikulu."
  16,110,"Mana toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khubalia abawuya nibakhasandibwa, mana nibalwana mana nibesumilisia, toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olunyuma lwa ako ni Omulesheli muno, Owetsimbabaasi po."